'From Squeak3.3alpha of 30 January 2002 [latest update: #4827] on 19 April 2002 at 8:42:02 am'!"Change Set:		ProcBrowTallyUI-nkDate:			17 April 2002Author:			Ned Konz(is the name small enough for Macs?)I noticed that the 'profile messages' choice in the ProcessBrowser no longer worked for the UI. This should fix that problem."!!ProcessBrowser methodsFor: 'stack list' stamp: 'nk 4/17/2002 14:52'!messageTally	| secString secs |	secString _ FillInTheBlank request: 'Profile for how many seconds?' initialAnswer: '4'.	secs _ secString asNumber asInteger.	(secs isNil			or: [secs isZero])		ifTrue: [^ self].	[ MessageTally spyOnProcess: selectedProcess forMilliseconds: secs * 1000 ] forkAt: selectedProcess priority + 1.! !